risks.risk_applicable:
The EQR shall include, as a minimum: 
1. Discussion of significant matters with the engagement partner; 
2. Review of the financial statements or other subject matter information and the proposed report; 
3. Review of selected working paper file documentation relating to the significant judgments the engagement team made and the conclusions it reached; and 
4. Evaluation of the conclusions reached in formulating the report and consideration of whether the proposed report is appropriate.
